      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 997.1 Carrera S, featuring the revered M97.01 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six. This example is mechanically superlative, exhibiting zero bore scoring and a verified IMS status. Power is delivered via a precise G97 6-speed manual transaxle, complemented by the factory Sport Chrono Package and PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) for optimized damping. The chassis remains rigid and communicative, with fresh bushings and Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber on lobster-claw alloys. Finished in a deep, factory-original paint with a high-gloss finish, the interior shows negligible bolster wear and crisp switchgear. This is a turn-key, enthusiast-maintained specimen for the discerning collector.",
